" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Motility testing on nonlactose fermenting gram negative rods",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 221px; height: 274px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Left tube: The nonmotile Shigella does not migrate away from the central stab line in the agar. Right tube: Motile Proteus produces visible opacification of the agar away from the central stab line. The color difference between the two samples is unrelated to the motility test.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
